        <p>
Find The Difference is a 3D Virtual Reality puzzle game developed for Oculus platforms, where players test their memory and observation skills by identifying missing objects across two versions of the same room. The game features 18 uniquely themed environments, such as bakeries, arcades, and living rooms, each crafted to challenge visual perception and attention to detail.        </p>
